Skin Nutrition Signs Network Marketing Deal

by Richard on January 4th, 2011

Skin Nutrition’s Australian joint venture company, Skin Nutrition Australia, signed a worldwide network marketing deal with Staunch International, a network sales specialist company based in Surfers Paradise, Australia. Staunch will market Skin Nutrition branded products through its worldwide membership base.
